21.body: Couchdb (and Pouchdb) is ID-based, and strongly recommends using ID for function. ID wll include: ";" separated version record type artist unique pot identifier (Date/Time) random 3 digit number Assumptions (not required) version only changes for incompatible records 0 is initial version record type p piece d depot pictures artist artist name Piece use creation ISO format UTC time random 3 digit number (rough tie-breaker)
